	<li>Must have hands-on experience in crop production, farm implements, irrigation and general agricultural practice</li>
	<li>Proven experience in growing sales within a defined area and influencing behavioural and strategic shifts required to grow the business</li>
	<li>Strong interpersonal and communication skills with the ability to engage effectively with farmers and distribution partners</li>
	<li>Must have a valid driver&rsquo;s license and be willing to travel extensively within the region</li>
